{"word":"G5178 - τυμπανίζω - tympanízō - toom-pan-id'-zo - Torture","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τυμπανίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tympanízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">toom-pan-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Torture</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாதிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to beat the drum or timbrel"},{"paragraph":"2. to torture with the tympanum, an instrument of punishment"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5180 - τύπτω - týptō - toop'-to/5180\">G5180</a> (meaning a <i>drum</i>, &ldquo;tympanum&rdquo;); to stretch on an instrument of <i>torture</i> resembling a drum, and thus <i>beat</i> to death: - torture.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}